## Interactive Features

[Only include this section if the chart supports interactive features such as tooltips or pointer events. Remove this section entirely if the chart has no interactive capabilities.]

### Tooltips

Enable interactive tooltips that display data information on hover:

<Source
	language="tsx"
	code={ `<[Component]
		data={ data }
		withTooltips={ true }
		renderTooltip={ ({ datum, color }) => (
			<div>
				<div>{ datum.label }: { datum.value }</div>
			</div>
		) }
	/>` }
/>

### Keyboard Navigation

Charts are fully keyboard accessible:
- **Tab**: Focus the chart
- **Arrow Keys**: Navigate between data points
- **Enter/Space**: Activate tooltips
- **Escape**: Close active tooltips

